title: Radio Control Car Action - April 2016
description:
English | 108 pages | PDF | 44.6 MB




Radio Control Car Action is dedicated to covering America's fastest growing hobby - radio control cars. Includes riveting reviews of new kits and major racing events that will keep the hobbyist informed of all the latest trends. You'll anticipate every issue including how-to articles and in-depth technical features that are helpful to both beginners and experienced modellers alike
